Thermon Group Holdings, Inc.

100 Thermon Drive 
San Marcos TX 78666 United States
Phone: +1 512-___-____
Fax: +1 512-___-____
http://www.thermon.com





10
Managers




35
IT employees




$7.6MEST.
IT Budget




Thermon Group Holdings, Inc. provides thermal engineered solutions for process industries worldwide.
The IT department for Thermon Group Holdings, Inc. operates out of the company's San Marcos, TX headquarters. The staff here is responsible for providing support to offices around the United States.

Software Development staff are responsible for the design and implementation… MoreThe IT department for Thermon Group Holdings, Inc. operates out of the company's San Marcos, TX headquarters. The staff here is responsible for providing support to offices around the United States.

Software Development staff are responsible for the design and implementation of the company's CompuTrace for Windows design software. A Director is responsible for the entire infrastructure.This team handles both internal and external software. The IT Help Desk assists with Active Directory management, networking issue resolution, messaging, desktop services, inventory management, and Citrix user management. 

The rest of the department handles data center operations, network security, telecommunications systems, and server administration.





