	CompuTrace Design Suite































Home



CompuTrace® Design Suite



CompuTrace® VT



CompuTrace® IT



CompuTrace® ST



TraceNet™ Command








CompuTrace® Design Suite
 Electric Heat Trace Design Software


 Thermon, a world leader in providing complete heat tracing solutions, has reset the standard in heat tracing design with its new CompuTrace Design Suite. This software package includes several new features and benefits that offer engineers the most comprehensive and robust heat tracing design tool on the market.


An easy-to-use “Quick Start Guide” will guide you through installation of CompuTrace Design Suite, and provide a graphical overview when using this software.





 





 



 
    Download CompuTrace® Design Suite


 
    Download CompuTrace® Design Suite Server Component





Minimum System Requirements

1.5 Ghz processor
1 Gigabyte RAM
100 Gigabyte hard disk
USB 2.0 port
Screen resolution 1280 x 768
Windows 7 or 8






Features and Benefits

Interactive circuit layout for piping segmentation
Numerous connection design possibilities
User defined components, insulation, pipes, valves, flanges, pumps and supports
User defined default circuit reduces repetitive design input
Ability to include electrical loads external to CompuTrace
Collaborate with multiple users on server projects
Filter BOM based on module, work package or area
Import data from Excel line list
User friendly interface








     To obtain the software on flash drive,
        contact Thermon.
        






